nested_items.description: The configuration managers returned by the request.

nested_items.name: ConfigurationDefinitionSummaries
nested_items.description: A summary of the Quick Setup configuration definition.

nested_items.name: FirstClassParameters

(string) ---
(string) ---

nested_items.name: Id
nested_items.description: The ID of the configuration definition.

nested_items.name: Type
nested_items.description: The type of the Quick Setup configuration used by the configuration definition.

nested_items.name: TypeVersion
nested_items.description: The version of the Quick Setup type used by the configuration definition.

nested_items.name: Description
nested_items.description: The description of the configuration.

nested_items.name: ManagerArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the Quick Setup configuration.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The name of the configuration.

nested_items.name: StatusSummaries
nested_items.description: Summaries of the state of the configuration manager. These summaries include an aggregate of the statuses from the configuration definition associated with the configuration manager. This includes deployment statuses, association statuses, drift statuses, health checks, and more.

nested_items.name: LastUpdatedAt
nested_items.description: The datetime stamp when the status was last updated.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The current status.

nested_items.name: StatusDetails
nested_items.description: Details about the status.
(string) ---
(string) ---

nested_items.name: StatusMessage
nested_items.description: When applicable, returns an informational message relevant to the current status and status type of the status summary object. We don't recommend implementing parsing logic around this value since the messages returned can vary in format.

nested_items.name: StatusType
nested_items.description: The type of a status summary.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token to use when requesting the next set of configuration managers. If there are no additional operations to return, the string is empty.
